{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/ios-simulator-screenshot/2021-02-04-ios-simulator-screenshot/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Won"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"01fb8731-3fcd-5e0d-801c-4d1e174c2147","excerpt":"How to take a screenshot and record a Video in iOS Simulator in Terminal  Open iOS Simulator Open Terminal.app Run below script to take a screenshot Run below…","html":"<h3>How to take a screenshot and record a Video in iOS Simulator in Terminal</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/bb051/simulator.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 189.1891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Demo\"\n        title=\"Demo\"\n        src=\"/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/fcda8/simulator.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/12f09/simulator.png 148w,\n/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/e4a3f/simulator.png 295w,\n/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/fcda8/simulator.png 590w,\n/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/efc66/simulator.png 885w,\n/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/c83ae/simulator.png 1180w,\n/static/b76e412b580e63416c42d8d99224c8ec/bb051/simulator.png 1212w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open iOS Simulator</li>\n<li>Open Terminal.app</li>\n<li>Run below script to take a screenshot</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">xcrun simctl io booted screenshot 1r.png</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Run below script to record a video and press CTRL + C to stop</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">xcrun simctl io booted recordVideo appPreview.mp4</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Additional commands</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">xcrun simctl list\nxcrun simctl addmedia booted ~/Desktop/sample.png\nxcrun simctl list <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> Booted <span class=\"token comment\"># list booted simulators</span>\nxcrun simctl <span class=\"token function\">shutdown</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$UUID</span>\nxcrun simctl erase <span class=\"token variable\">$UUID</span>\npbcopy ~/Desktop/sample.txt\nxcrun simctl pbpaste booted\nxcrun simctl openurl booted <span class=\"token string\">\"https://developer.apple.com\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to take a screenshot and record a Video in iOS Simulator in Terminal","date":"February 04, 2021","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ios-simulator-screenshot/2021-02-04-ios-simulator-screenshot/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tips/take-ios-simulator-screenshot-from-terminal/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to take a screenshot and record a Video in iOS Simulator in Terminal"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/xcode-shortcuts/2021-02-27-xcode-shortcuts/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"생산성 향상을 위한 Xcode 단축키들: ⌘ + R 을 넘어서"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["240262808","2841359383"]}